Executive Profile
Harry N. Pefanis  President, COO & Director - Plains All American GP LLC, Plains All American Pipeline, L.P.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 6 Board Members in 6 different organizations across 9 different industries.See Board Relationships60$317,340As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Harry N. Pefanis serves as President and Chief Operating Officer of Plains Pipeline L.P. Mr. Pefanis is responsible for executing Plains Pipeline's ategy, oversees its day-to-day operations, coordinating the many disciplines within identifying areas for future expansion. Mr. Pefanis has been President and Chief Operating Officer of PAA GP Holdings LLC, the General Partner of Plains GP Holdings, L.P. and Plains All American GP LLC since July 2013. Mr. Pefanis serves ... as the Chief Operating Officer and President of Plains Holdings Gp LLC. He has been  President and  Chief Operating Officer of Plains All American GP LLC GP at Plains All American Pipeline, L.P.  since September  1998 and has been its Director. He served as Executive Officer of Vulcan Energy Corporation. Mr. Pefanis served as the President at Plains Marketing, L.P. He served as the President of Bluewater Gas Storage LLC. He served as an Executive Vice President, Midstream of Plains Resources from May 1998 to May 2001. He served as Senior Vice President of Plains Resources from February 1996 to May 1998; Vice President of Products Marketing from 1988 to February 1996; Manager of Products Marketing from 1987 to 1988 and Special Assistant for Corporate Planning from 1983 to 1987. He served as President of several former midstream subsidiaries of Plains Resources until 1998. He has been the Vice Chairman of PNGS GP LLC, General Partner of PAA Natural Gas Storage, LLC since January 2010. He has been a Director at American Petroleum Institute Inc. since January 2011. He serves as a Member of Executive Advisory Board of C.T. Bauer College of Business. He has been a Director of PAA GP Holdings LLC, the General Partner of Plains GP Holdings, L.P. since February 21, 2017. Mr. Pefanis served as a Director of PAAP's former general partner.Read Full Background




