Insider Activity


Individual




Harry N. Pefanis



Mr. Harry N. Pefanis is President & Chief Operating Officer at Plains GP Holdings LP, President & Chief Operating Officer at PAA GP Holdings LLC, President & Chief Operating Officer at Plains All American Pipeline LP, President & Chief Operating Officer at Plains All American GP LLC, and President & Chief Operating Officer at PAA GP LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at PAA Natural Gas Storage LLC, PNGS GP LLC, Settoon Towing LLC, and PAA Natural Gas Storage LP.
Mr. Pefanis was previously employed as Executive Vice President-Midstream Division by Plains Resources, Inc. He also served on the board at PAA.



