Key Executives
                > Harry N. Pefanis
            
Harry N. Pefanis, Director, President and Chief Operating Officer



Profile
Connections






Biography



    Harry N. Pefanis has served as President and Chief Operating Officer since our formation in 1998. He was also a director of our former general partner. In addition, he was Executive Vice President-Midstream of Plains Resources from May 1998 to May 2001. He previously served Plains Resources as: Senior Vice President from February 1996 until May 1998; Vice President-Products Marketing from 1988 to February 1996; Manager of Products Marketing from 1987 to 1988; and Special Assistant for Corporate Planning from 1983 to 1987. Mr. Pefanis was also President of several former midstream subsidiaries of Plains Resources until our formation. Mr. Pefanis is a director of Settoon Towing. Mr. Pefanis is also President and Chief Operating Officer of GP Holdings, which is the general partner of PAGP. On February 16, 2017, the board of directors (the Board) of PAA GP Holdings LLC (PAGP GP) appointed Harry N. Pefanis to the Board.
    





